Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,(avant)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种感情叫做恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是动物所拥有的很一般的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧 究竟为何而生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐惧 也分为动物本能产生的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和思考产生的逻辑性的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当一个人遇到比自己更加强大的存在 而且认识到自己无力反抗时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或者是遇到未知的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种无知就会很容易地唤醒恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当直面恐惧时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们会采取几种行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挣扎 反抗 逃亡 接受等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 当遇到迪奥大人的时候则会涌现一种新的冲动——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快感！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦对恐惧所唤醒的快感食髓知味 人会怎样行动？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在跟乔斯达他们同乘一架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定不可能平安到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独角仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是锹形虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.49,0:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布德尔 那是替身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就出现新的替身使者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能 昆虫形态的替身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲到座位的阴影里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在…在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JoJo 在你的头部的右边！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:59.52,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}そして、集いしスターダスト
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:06.08,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}100年目の目醒めに呼ばれて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:10.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}男たちは向かう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:16.58,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}時の砂を越えるJourney
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:22.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}鎖のよう連なる 絡み合う宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:22.71,OP_CH,NTP,440,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}カルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:28.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}白金で断つ運命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:28.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,200,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:28.93,OP_CH,NTP,200,0,0,,{\blur2\an2\fs24}さだめ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:32.74,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Stand up! Stand up! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.98,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}打ち込むのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.60,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}All right now All right now All right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:42.09,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}誇りのBullet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.39,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}Break you down Break you down Break you down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:53.28,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an2}拳放つ 聖なるヴィジョン Stand Proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:59.52,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百年沉睡的苏醒在召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:06.08,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星尘遥呼 相继汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:10.95,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}男子汉一行已启程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:16.58,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏上穿越时间的沙漠之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:22.71,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宿命 如同一串错综连横的枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:28.93,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挥起白金斩断命运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.98,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迸射而出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:42.09,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是高傲的弹头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:53.28,OP_CH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铁拳百裂 神圣的幻象 Stand Proud!
